content: So far I haven't encountered the time limit most over reviews are talking about (maybe the devs took it out). There certainly are still some freemium like features that encourage you to spend more money. But they aren't 100% necessary, even if it feels that way at times. Overall I've found it an enjoyable sequel to the original. So far.
